dialogue.text: Hello, it seems you're using low quality setting.
Due to optimization concerns in week 2, every dialogue in this setting will have a single portrait for each character.
We hope you can understand, have fun.
Hey, you two okay?
Well yeah, but I think you have some explaining to do.
What he said! Who are you? Why are you protecting us?
My name's Nathan, and I'm the co-owner of Galaxii Games.
But unfortunately, in recent years, Nova's become so obsessed with money.
She's not who she used to be...
But that aside, we should be safe in this alleyway.
I asked my friend to try and reason with them, he isn't big on what they've become either.
I just hope Nova doesn't fire him...
So what now? Do we wait for him to come here and tell us what went down?
Pretty mu-
FR-THREAT DETECTED.
Geez...
Hey, you were able to defeat that thing before, reckon you can do it again?
Yeah, but I'm not sure how we activated his Karaoke Mode last time...
Aaron, 'Your mom'.
KARAOKE MODE. ACCEPTED.
